'''硼化钽'''（化学式：TaB，TaB<sub>2</sub>）是[[钽|钽]]和[[硼|硼]]组成的[[化合物|化合物]]，它的[[硬度|硬度]]极高。

==性质==
TaB和TaB<sub>2</sub>薄片和晶体的[[维氏硬度试验|维氏硬度]]为30GPa。<ref name=TaB/><ref name=otani/><ref name=okada/> 在700℃以下时，这些物质很耐氧化和酸腐蚀，性质是稳定的。<ref name=TaB/><ref name=okada/>

TaB<sub>2</sub>与大多数二硼化物（AlB<sub>2</sub>, MgB<sub>2</sub>等）具有相同的六方形结构。<ref>{{cite journal | last=Chen | first=Xing-Qiu | last2=Fu | first2=C. L. | last3=Krčmar | first3=M. | last4=Painter | first4=G. S. | title=Electronic and Structural Origin of Ultraincompressibility of5dTransition-Metal DiboridesMB2(M=W, Re, Os) | journal=Physical Review Letters | publisher=American Physical Society (APS) | volume=100 | issue=19 | date=2008-05-16 | issn=0031-9007 | doi=10.1103/physrevlett.100.196403 | page=196403}}</ref> 这些硼化物具有以下分类空间：TaB（[[正交晶系|正交晶系]]，{{tsl|en|Thallium(I) iodide||碘化亚铊}}型，CMCM），Ta<sub>5</sub>B<sub>6</sub> （Cmmm）, Ta<sub>3</sub>B<sub>4</sub> （Immm）, TaB<sub>2</sub> （[[六方晶系|六方晶系]], [[二硼化铝|二硼化铝]]型，P6/mmm）。<ref name=okada/>

== 制取 ==
采用[[區域熔煉|区域熔炼法]]可制得TaB，Ta<sub>5</sub>B<sub>6</sub>，Ta<sub>3</sub>B<sub>4</sub>或TaB<sub>2</sub>单晶（直径约1cm，长度约6cm）。<ref name=otani>{{cite journal | last=Otani | first=S | last2=Korsukova | first2=M.M | last3=Mitsuhashi | first3=T | title=Floating zone growth and high-temperature hardness of NbB2 and TaB2 single crystals | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-crystal-growth_1998-12_194_3-4/page/430 | journal=Journal of Crystal Growth | publisher=Elsevier BV | volume=194 | issue=3-4 | year=1998 | issn=0022-0248 | doi=10.1016/s0022-0248(98)00691-5 | pages=430–433}}</ref><ref name=okada>{{cite journal | last=Okada | first=Shigeru | last2=Kudou | first2=Kunio | last3=Higashi | first3=Iwarni | last4=Lundström | first4=Torsten | title=Single crystals of TaB, Ta5B6, Ta3B4 and TAB2, as obtained from high-temperature metal solutions, and their properties | url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-crystal-growth_1993_128_1-4/page/1120 | journal=Journal of Crystal Growth | publisher=Elsevier BV | volume=128 | issue=1-4 | year=1993 | issn=0022-0248 | doi=10.1016/s0022-0248(07)80109-6 | pages=1120–1124}}</ref>

使用TaCl<sub>5</sub>-BCl<sub>3</sub>-H<sub>2</sub>-Ar混合气体在540~800°C范围内时沉积硼化钽薄片。在源气流量比（BCl<sub>3</sub>/TaCl<sub>5</sub>）为6，温度在600°C以上时沉积TaB<sub>2</sub>（单晶）。在BCl<sub>3</sub>/TaCl<sub>5</sub> = 2/4 ，温度在600-700°C时沉积TaB（单晶）。<ref name=TaB>{{cite journal | last=Motojima | first=Seiji | last2=Kito | first2=Kazuhito | last3=Sugiyama | first3=Kohzo | title=Low-temperature deposition of TaB and TaB2 by chemical vapor deposition | journal=Journal of Nuclear Materials | publisher=Elsevier BV | volume=105 | issue=2-3 | year=1982 | issn=0022-3115 | doi=10.1016/0022-3115(82)90383-x | pages=262–268}}</ref>

以NaBH<sub>4</sub>和Ta<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub>为原料，在700~900°C下，摩尔质量比M:B为1:4时，在氩气中还原30分钟，就可以合成TaB<sub>2</sub>。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Zoli|first1=Luca|last2=Galizia|first2=Pietro|last3=Silvestroni|first3=Laura|last4=Sciti|first4=Diletta|title=Synthesis of group IV and V metal diboride nanocrystals via borothermal reduction with sodium borohydride|journal=Journal of the American Ceramic Society|volume=101|issue=6|pages=2627–2637|date=2018-01-23|doi=10.1111/jace.15401|url=https://zenodo.org/record/1292491/files/zoli%20JACERS.pdf|access-date=2020-07-22|archive-date=2019-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190504065322/https://zenodo.org/record/1292491/files/zoli%20JACERS.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

:Ta<sub>2</sub>O<sub>5</sub> + 6.5 NaBH<sub>4</sub> → 2 TaB<sub>2</sub> + 4 Na(g,l) + 2.5 NaBO<sub>2</sub>+ 13 H<sub>2</sub>(g)

